## bounded-inspection-pattern
  peek <file> --count           # 1. learn size
  peek <file> --grep <pattern>  # 2. locate target line
  peek <file> --start N --end M # 3. bounded read
  peek <file> --all             # 4. escape hatch (token-expensive, use sparingly)

